                     <interp inst="t18300415-204-off1136" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the 15th of March, 1 umbrella, value 3s., and 1 stick, value 6d.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18300415-204-victim1819" type="victimName">
                     Christian 
                     Bergstrom
                  <interp inst="t18300415-204-victim1819" type="surname" value="Bergstrom"></interp>
